rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard Acedia collapsed. Alst
is in a terrible state...

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm sure you all have things you
need to do, but please be careful.

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0003
rows.name:
Once it's all settled... I know it's
just a simple little village, but please
stop by and tell us all about it.

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0005
rows.name:
Be careful out there. And make sure
you come back to this village.

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0007
rows.name:
I'll make some Fragrant Vegetable
Mott Rolls and wait for you.
